N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 272.2 - Fee

State Regulations

Each application shall be accompanied by a certified check, payable to the Commissioner of General Services, State of New York, for the sum
of $50 to cover the cost and expenses of the investigation incident to such
application. This payment shall be considered a fee and no part of such payment
shall be refunded. Notes
